    <content contentuid="hf7ce1679g6ea7ge690ge8f5gf96b19ea138d" version="1">Arcane Adept</content>
    <content contentuid="h7b34be89g740bg9ec1g3af5g847fbaa20d1b" version="1">You gain a +[1] bonus to &lt;LSTag Tooltip="SpellDifficultyClass"&gt;Spell Save DC&lt;/LSTag&gt;, spell &lt;LSTag Tooltip="AttackRoll"&gt;attack rolls&lt;/LSTag&gt;, and spell damage.</content>
    <content contentuid="h7b44d93eg742dg1da7g7a87g7eb47f4636fd" version="1">Archer</content>
    <content contentuid="h2ada8c5ag7ce0gcbe5g45e4g0d23d9f37187" version="1">You are proficient with all bows, and gain a +[1] bonus to &lt;LSTag Tooltip="RangedWeaponAttack"&gt;ranged weapon attacks&lt;/LSTag&gt; and damage.</content>
    <content contentuid="hac8e2fc0gbad6gfa83gc083ge6e2b2ff218c" version="1">Light-Fingered</content>
    <content contentuid="h599b6d56gf1b2gf8f4g5698gc1427ee10ddf" version="1">You gain &lt;LSTag Tooltip="Expertise"&gt;Expertise&lt;/LSTag&gt; in &lt;LSTag Tooltip="SleightOfHand"&gt;Sleight of Hand&lt;/LSTag&gt;.</content>
    <content contentuid="h067af7e3g3d32gb6bdg9683g2ec3c9404d02" version="1">Persuasive</content>
    <content contentuid="h28b0de37gdfd2g7fdbge0dfgaf9ac3f2b895" version="1">You gain &lt;LSTag Tooltip="Expertise"&gt;Expertise&lt;/LSTag&gt; in &lt;LSTag Tooltip="Persuasion"&gt;Persuasion&lt;/LSTag&gt;.</content>
    <content contentuid="h1a4ae6c6g5bebgfa29g5529g4360a9bba332" version="1">Weaponmaster</content>
    <content contentuid="hb7b2b7acg08e9g1fc5g3317g208c2f73dbd0" version="1">You are proficient with all melee martial weapons, and gain a +[1] bonus to &lt;LSTag Tooltip="MeleeWeaponAttack"&gt;melee weapon attacks&lt;/LSTag&gt; and damage.</content>
    <content contentuid="h838c3265gd53egd906g507agfd7d319d8c42" version="1">Action Surge</content>
    <content contentuid="h1c2abea4gf2d5g85d4gfda8g213d5fb8ef50" version="1">Immediately gain an extra &lt;LSTag Tooltip="Action"&gt;action&lt;/LSTag&gt; to use this turn.</content>
    <content contentuid="h8476ee02g6de8g801dg2d85ge405b856ce0b" version="1">Battle Magic</content>
    <content contentuid="h3d7f50bdgc643g9c31gf884ge4329ca8b39c" version="1">After making a weapon or unarmed attack, you can cast a spell as a &lt;LSTag Type="ActionResource" Tooltip="BonusActionPoint"&gt;bonus action&lt;/LSTag&gt;.</content>
    <content contentuid="hecd23950g34d6g3dfegc01bg86e875fe1ffc" version="1">Cunning Actions</content>
    <content contentuid="h43fed24eg5456gf7b9gb4b7gd42ec2a1a7f0" version="1">They'll never see you coming, until it's too late. As a bonus action, you can use &lt;LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Dash_CunningAction"&gt;Cunning Action: Dash&lt;/LSTag&gt;, &lt;LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Hide_BonusAction"&gt;Cunning Action: Hide&lt;/LSTag&gt;, or &lt;LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Disengage_CunningAction"&gt;Cunning Action: Disengage&lt;/LSTag&gt;.</content>
    <content contentuid="h773b01c1g97c0g10b1g92d9g5552939915a9" version="1">Fleet of Foot</content>
    <content contentuid="hd1100b9cgf4dbg7cedg6535g1ea3bd2129c9" version="1">&lt;LSTag Tooltip="MovementSpeed"&gt;Movement speed&lt;/LSTag&gt; increased by [1].</content>
    <content contentuid="hd6f689d7g6686ga18dg3892g4183ac26dd12" version="1">Resilience</content>
    <content contentuid="h4bea5f36gdeadg5aadgf237g9f4671afb5de" version="1">You shrug off attacks, taking [1] less damage from all sources.</content>
    <content contentuid="h6815fb2agedf3g3bcfg5479g62e94efe9c43" version="1">Fire Walk</content>
    <content contentuid="h6060ed13gbb3dgf5edgb9fcg60b582bd390a" version="1">You step through the hells, reappearing in another location.</content>
    <content contentuid="h815151f9g88ceg0a4bgafd4g88b303056687" version="1">Fire Walk</content>
    <content contentuid="ha3736fa3gb0e2ge4d3gb263g4cef4c1beb34" version="1">You step through the hells, reappearing in another location.</content>
    <content contentuid="hfad3fadag99f0g0693gab38g16191107eb2f" version="1">Misty Step</content>
    <content contentuid="h9ac6f6a9ga395g48adgcad8g715773f0d05c" version="1">Surrounded by silver mist, you teleport to an unoccupied space you can see.</content>
    <content contentuid="hd0c83a1dg731bgdad8g8a40g11a358fd3068" version="1">Wilderness Explorer</content>
    <content contentuid="hc4989ad0gf692g4b28g7f79g90c81f92849f" version="1">You have become an expert at moving through the wilderness. &lt;LSTag Type="Status" Tooltip="DIFFICULT_TERRAIN"&gt;Difficult Terrain&lt;/LSTag&gt; no longer slows you down, and you can't slip on grease or ice.</content>
    <content contentuid="h88c9a9aeg1851gc942g94a1g64d7d0301c1d" version="1">Empowered Spells</content>
    <content contentuid="h6c984b96gc0cege15cg6237g8f73ceb0c95a" version="1">When you cast a damaging spell, add your &lt;LSTag Tooltip="SpellcastingAbilityModifier"&gt;Spellcasting Modifier&lt;/LSTag&gt; to the damage it deals.</content>
    <content contentuid="h8e39161cg2951g1b65g699dg1173da593e0a" version="1">Volley</content>
    <content contentuid="h01f8f5aagd28cg7c33ga1e6gcccefb81173d" version="1">Strike multiple foes at once. You gain &lt;LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Target_Volley"&gt;Volley&lt;/LSTag&gt; and &lt;LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Whirlwind"&gt;Whirlwind&lt;/LSTag&gt;</content>
